text: Rima Yussef is a Lebanese singer and songwriter.https://www.arabnews.com/node/2456231/lifestyle She is known for her work in the UAE. She was born in the Ivory Coast but moved to Lebanon at a young age. Yussef began her musical career at a young age, performing in school and on television. She later enrolled in a music academy. She is also known for her single "Mghayarni," which is a ballad with a modern twist. == References == Category:Lebanese singers Category:Arab people Category:Muslims by nationality
